    "description": "<p>Your understanding of psionics is unparalleled, and combined with your use of them has permanently altered your consciousness. &nbsp;You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Whenever you roll high enough on a psi die to regain one while at your maximum number, you gain inspiration.</li>\n<li>You gain an expertise die on all intelligence, wisdom, and charisma saving throws.</li>\n<li>You gain a bonus exertion pool equal to your intelligence modifier. &nbsp;These exertion points may only be spend on awakened mind maneuvers. &nbsp;It refills on short rest just like your standard exertion pool.</li>\n</ul>",
